high_descs: Move across the room to the counter on the right side of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, and move to the silver counter top on the left side of the sink.
Slice the potato that is near the back of the counter.
Turn around and move the counter on the left side of the stove.
Place the knife in the black pan shaped like a hexagon.
Turn around and move across the room to the left side of the sink with the silver counter top.
Pick up a piece of potato off of the counter.
Move to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave. Turn on the microwave and cook the potato. Remove the cooked potato and close the microwave door.
Move across the room to the counter top on the left side of the stove.
Place the cooked potato slice on the counter on the right side of the pan.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato to cook in the microwave to be placed on the counter top near the stove.
